fields.content_text_top: Antique iron and metal artifacts, speedometers, dashboards, tools, and hardware are creatively fashioned into the most unimaginable table lamps making them a must have for any side table.  The wooden candle stands are crafted from antique salvaged architectural columns and panels making them unique accents. Cutwork metal candle holders and antique oil lanterns too will make prodigious accents.

fields.seo_title: Unique Selection of Indoor Wall Lights - Wood Sense Interiors
fields.seo_description: The perfect light for the washroom with a one of a kind vanity or any dull wall. The fine metal lights will complement your space with the fine cutwork to filter out the light creating shadow designs on the walls.
fields.seo_keywords: indoor wall lights
fields.name: Wall Lights
fields.content_text_top: These are the perfect light for the washroom with a one of a kind vanity or any unadorned wall. The fine metal lights will complement your space with the fine cutwork to filter out the light creating shadow designs on the walls.

fields.seo_title: Metal Wall Art - Paintings, Panels & Decor
fields.seo_description: Hand painted, hand welded art pieces depicting automobile theme are a must have for the Male gender to grace his Man Cave. There is an assortment of selection from the auto theme to horses, flags, highway routes and cityscapes. These pieces are creative designs illustrated by talented artists and are truly in vogue.
fields.seo_keywords: metal art, metal art decor, metal wall art
fields.name: Metal Art Paintings
fields.content_text_top: Hand painted, hand welded art pieces depicting automobile themes are a must have for the Man Cave. We have an extensive selection from the auto theme to horses, flags, highway routes and cityscapes. These pieces are creative designs created by talented artists and are truly in vogue.

fields.seo_title: Unique Wall Mirrors - Reclaimed Wood, Industrial Style & Antique
fields.seo_description: Mirrors add style and sparkle to a wall. Out mirrors range from antique window and door frames to modern live edge frames. Visit our showroom to view all mirrors.
fields.seo_keywords: unique mirrors, reclaimed wood mirrors, antique mirrors
fields.name: Mirrors
fields.content_text_top: Mirrors add style and sparkle to a wall. These reflective surfaces help a room feel brighter, airier and larger by creating an opulent atmosphere. Our mirrors range from antique window and door frames to modern live edge frames. Carved panels are creatively utilized to make the most unusual mirror frames in sizes that cover small walls in tiny powder rooms to large oversized hallway mirrors. We have rustic natural teak frames in various shapes and sizes, brass fitted, and carved stencil fitted frames - the range of mirrors at Wood Sense Interiors is extensive.

fields.seo_title: Indoor & Outdoor Statues & Figurines - Wood Sense Interiors
fields.seo_description: Wood Sense carries the largest selection of statues of Buddha and Ganesh in Solid wood, Brass and stone ranging from tiny figurines to large life size figures. Brass statues of Buddha and Ganesh studded with natural Jade, Turquoise and Lapis gems in different poses are strikingly stunning art pieces. We also carry statues of Horses and Elephants in various sizes and styles.
fields.seo_keywords: indoor statues, outdoor statues, indoor figurines, outdoor figurines
fields.name: Statues
fields.content_text_top: One way to instantly add elegance, sophistication, and a classical touch to any room is to introduce a bust into your decor. Sculptural representations of religious iconography such as Buddha and Ganesh (the elephant head God) create a calming influence in a room. Wood Sense carries the largest selection of statues of Buddha and Ganesh in solid wood, brass and stone ranging from tiny figurines to larger than life sized figures. Brass statues of Buddha and Ganesh studded with natural coral, Turquoise and Lapis gems in different poses are strikingly stunning art pieces. We also carry statues of horses and elephants in various sizes and poses.

fields.seo_title: Silk Drapes & Panels with Blackout & Regular Lining
fields.seo_description: We carry Thai Silk panels in royal shades with blackout lining to give your space complete privacy. Dupion Silk panels with just regular lining in an array of colours are also part of our selection.
fields.seo_keywords: drapes, silk panels
fields.name: Drapes
fields.content_text_top: Curtains dress a window by adding the final touch of elegance to a room. We carry Thai Silk panels in royal shades with blackout lining to give your space complete privacy. Dupion Silk panels with regular lining in an array of colours are also part of our selection. The simple yet classy Linen panels in neutral prints and solids again lined are a subtle choice. All styles of panels are rod pocket with a standard size of 50” width by 96” length.

fields.seo_title: Solid Wood Wall Art - Wood Sense Interiors
fields.seo_description: Solid Wood hand carved wall pieces in horizontal and vertical designs with illustrations of Various Indian Gods or just beautiful carvings from antique reminiscent are artistic pieces to decorate a blank wall.
fields.seo_keywords: wood wall art, wall panels, solid wood wall art
fields.name: Wall Panels & Carved Panels
fields.content_text_top: Solid Wood hand carved wall pieces in horizontal and vertical orientations with depictions of various Indian Gods or just beautiful carvings from antiques reminiscent of by gone days are some of what you'll find at Wood Sense Interiors. The mosaicked teak wall panels on a 4’ by 8’ panel can be imaginatively used to cover a bare wall yet have limitless design possibilities including headboards and fireplace mantles. These can be customised by cutting them to fit your space. Free standing teak panels on a solid base are novel options for room dividers. Also part of this range are hand painted colorful canvases in oil with Indian themes finished in solid wood frames.

fields.seo_title: Unique & Decorative Wall Hooks - Wood Sense Interiors
fields.seo_description: Wall hooks for hanging jackets, hats or kids backpacks is a must to have in every home. We carry the most beautiful range of hooks for this need from solid wood carved elephant heads to simple carved ones. We've been proudly serving Oakville, Mississauga, Brampton, Burlington, Hamilton & Toronto for over 22 years.
fields.seo_keywords: wall hooks, unique wall hooks
fields.name: Hooks
fields.content_text_top: Wall hooks for hanging jackets, hats or kids' backpacks are a must have in every home. We carry the most beautiful range of hooks for this need from solid wood carved elephant heads to free form teak logs. The antique panels from salvaged architectural pieces made into hooks are the most exquisite you would ever see. These make stunning wall décor even when not holding any items.

fields.seo_title: Unique Wooden Decorative Boxes & Chests - Wood Sense Interiors
fields.seo_description: A Panoply of Solid wood boxes in assorted sizes, shapes and designs make a selection that is elusive to choose from. Brass fitted designs to hand carved incised designs, these boxes will hold all your valuable treasures or simply decorate the coffee table. The trinkets range from replica wooden rifles to hand painted metal urns and brass locks to antique treasures.
fields.seo_keywords: home decor, wooden bokes, tresure chests
fields.name: Boxes & Trinkets
fields.content_text_top: An abundance of solid wood boxes in assorted sizes, shapes and designs makes a selection that is difficult to choose from. with brass fitted designs and hand carved incised designs, these boxes will hold all your valuable treasures or simply decorate the coffee table. The trinkets range from replica wooden rifles to hand painted metal urns, brass locks to antique treasures.

fields.content_text_top: You will find the most unique, one of a kind, eclectic items at Wood Sense Interiors.

fields.content:
Save 10% on Rustic Elegance at WoodSense Interiors' Live Edge Furniture Sales Event!



Looking for unique and elegant furniture pieces that combine contemporary living with old-world charm? Look no further than WoodSense Interiors!

Our furniture is built with the finest woods, including Sheesham, Teak wood, and Rosewood, with a new product line made from the root of the teak wood tree. Our Live Edge Furniture Sales Event offers a fantastic opportunity to save 10% on all live edge items. Each piece is finished with eco-friendly materials to ensure that naturalness, elegance, and character are retained. Our earthy lifestyle store is a vibrant mix of created and curated pieces, an artful blend of the quirky and the contemporary.

Visit us now and explore our magnificent pieces of art that combine the best of history with contemporary living!

fields.text: I love this furniture store! My husband and I searched for a bedroom furniture for weeks. We researched 10 other furniture stores in the area. No other retailer came anywhere close in terms of value, selection, quality, uniqueness and service. We love our new furniture and we'll save time by shopping here first next time! I highly recommend.
fields.author: Jessica

fields.text: Superb quality solid wood furniture well worth every dollar I spent. Sales team is very knowledgeable and friendly. They made me feel special and organized same day delivery. Truly one of a kind store. I love the natural live edge dinning table I bought along with a reclaimed teak entertainment unit with antique doors.. Very high quality seasoned wood Strongly recommend.
fields.author: Steve

fields.text: Wow walking through here is like being in an art gallery. So many unique and beautiful pieces from around the world. Owners are true gentlemen.
fields.author: Nikil

fields.text: Gorgeous hand made imported furniture! Loves the store and the staff! Very helpful and we're very happy with our purchase!

fields.text: Buying from this store for the last fifteen years. My entire house has been furnished with unique  antique solid sheesham and teak wood furniture.The compliments we have received on the decor of our house have been overwhelming. Strongly recommended!
fields.author: Mohit

fields.text: One of the best furniture store I have ever visited.  Excellent quality and after sales service.I recommend this store in a heartbeat.
fields.author: Vic

fields.text:
We have been shopping for a live edge table for over a year...happened to do a Google search on local stores that sold them, and although Wood Sense's website isn't the greatest to navigate or gather information from, the pieces at the store are INCREDIBLE...I don't think a picture on a website could do justice to the store and the amazing pieces contained within!
Worth the visit...we walked in, and purchased the most incredible 10 ft. live edge table within 10 minutes! Friendliest and most knowledgeable staff, delivery was fast (and early!). We had a bit of minor damage during the delivery process, but a quick call to the store and staff was back at our house within 3 hours to fix it on the spot! Overall a fabulous shopping experience! Would highly recommend to anyone...thanks Wood Sense!

fields.seo_description: A furniture store that is all about solid wood. Our furniture is artistically built with the finest woods including Sheesham, Teak wood and Rosewood along with our new product line made with the root of the teak wood tree. Proudly serving Oakville, Mississauga, Brampton, Burlington, Hamilton & Toronto for over 22 years.
fields.seo_keywords: solid wood furniture, Sheesham wood, Teak wood, Rosewood
fields.banner_text: WHY SHOP AT WOOD SENSE INTERIORS
fields.content:
Wood Sense Interiors is all about solid wood. Our furniture is artistically built with the finest woods including Sheesham, Teak wood and Rosewood along with our new product line made with the root of the teak wood tree.

All the solid woods used are kiln dried and pressure-treated. Our wood is a hard wood with a firm compact texture and is extremely durable. Each piece is finished by eco-friendly materials that ensure the naturalness, elegance and character are retained.

The earthy Wood Sense Interiors is a lifestyle store with a vibrant mix of created and curated pieces, an artful blend of the quirky and the contemporary. We invite you to explore our collective cultural and historical nostalgia. From British-Mughal-reminiscent bronze lanterns and intricately painted wooden trunks to eclectically detailed furniture and vintage wall hangings, the store is a glorious blend of the old and the new, a reminder of times that are at the same time distant yet wholly relevant.

Interior designs at Wood Sense Interiors are narratives in their own right, each detail deliberate, each piece has a story. Luxury meets old-world charm in these magnificent pieces of art that combine the best of history with contemporary living. You are bound to find the right piece of furniture in the captivating collection of endearing original selection.
